page.title: 10Home LIfe Gipsey Bridge
page.content: {Interview with an insurance salesman. I get up at 9 o'clock and for breakfast I have 2 pieces of toast and some marmalade . Very occasionally I watch Breakfast T.V. which I find very interesting. I work at home in the morning doing paper work and have my dinner at about 1 o'clock,it is usually a sandwich or two.In the afternoon if I have got all my work done I do some gardening.On Tuesdays and Thursdays my wife and I both go out selling insurance. After tea I spend a lot of time phoning people that I am trying to sell insurance to. Then I usually watch some T.V., I always watch Calender, the local commercial channel news.Then I like to watch a film.I go to bed at about midnight or one o'clock.
